description: "Add new campaign on 3 planets (still WIP:)\n
The mod is focused on a difficulty slightly higher than the main game and follows the game design principles of the original Mindustry\n
Currently, the mod contains 6 sectors of the first of three planets. The development is delayed, but it has not been abandoned. I hope to complete the first sector of the second planet by 2027, which is planned to follow the 10 sector of the first planet.\n
Please rate me on github!"
